<p>AWS Cost Optimization</p>

<h1 id="summary">Summary</h1>
<p>Intuit spends ~$225m annually on AWS hosting. Continually optimizing the hosting cost through actionable insights and savings opportunities is one of the key deliverables for Cloud Engineering &amp; Operations team. As part of this effort, the team is constantly analysing design and utilization efficiencies across Intuit accounts, automating the recommendations and providing insights through cost optimization dashboards.</p>

